40:22.649 --> 40:25.385
who Angelo's source
at the hospital is.

40:25.419 --> 40:27.487
Call me when you can.

40:32.426 --> 40:34.594
John: Huh.

40:36.597 --> 40:40.333
Wow, will you look at that?

40:42.136 --> 40:43.403
It's, uh, cool, right?

40:43.437 --> 40:46.439
You know it's bad enough they
trash their own neighborhoods,

40:46.473 --> 40:48.941
now they come down here
and pull this crap?

40:48.976 --> 40:50.109
<i>And guess who gets to clean up?</i>

40:50.144 --> 40:53.112
Me. Eh, it's good
that you're here.

40:53.147 --> 40:55.815
I got paint and rollers in the back.

40:55.849 --> 40:59.185
You can tell me all about your
French project while we work.

40:59.219 --> 41:02.688
